00:41:07,656 --> 00:41:09,095
You kept playing with those threads.

832
00:41:09,095 --> 00:41:10,736
How can I focus like this?

833
00:41:14,216 --> 00:41:15,025
I'm done.

834
00:41:17,016 --> 00:41:18,535
Does this shirt cost
tens of thousands as well

835
00:41:18,535 --> 00:41:19,416
when it looks this cheap?

836
00:41:21,656 --> 00:41:24,496
I ordered this from Taobao.

837
00:41:24,496 --> 00:41:26,055
It's meant for people
to wear to food stalls.

838
00:41:26,256 --> 00:41:27,496
It costs 55 yuan

839
00:41:27,496 --> 00:41:29,335
from top to bottom.
And, it's disposable.

840
00:41:29,456 --> 00:41:30,375
By the way,

841
00:41:30,375 --> 00:41:31,855
it's 80 yuan if you include

842
00:41:32,095 --> 00:41:33,216
this disposable bottle as well.

843
00:41:33,375 --> 00:41:34,896
What? You use Taobao too?

844
00:41:35,256 --> 00:41:36,696
I had no choice. You forced me to do it.

845
00:41:37,375 --> 00:41:38,416
That's pretty good.

846
00:41:38,535 --> 00:41:40,335
Share the link with me later.

847
00:41:43,416 --> 00:41:44,656
By the way, I have
something to tell you.

848
00:41:44,656 --> 00:41:46,535
The Dragon Boat Festival
is a public holiday.

849
00:41:46,855 --> 00:41:48,615
Our tuition class

850
00:41:48,615 --> 00:41:49,496
will be suspended for the time being.

851
00:41:49,736 --> 00:41:50,656
But why?

852
00:41:51,055 --> 00:41:52,135
Are you going on a trip?

853
00:41:52,855 --> 00:41:54,896
I'm going to join the TCM forum.

854
00:41:55,256 --> 00:41:56,696
But your name wasn't included

855
00:41:56,696 --> 00:41:57,535
in the name list.

856
00:41:57,696 --> 00:41:59,295
Besides, people won't invite

857
00:41:59,295 --> 00:42:01,016
half-baked physicians like us.

858
00:42:01,016 --> 00:42:02,016
This time,

859
00:42:02,535 --> 00:42:05,176
I'm going there because
the organiser invited me.

860
00:42:05,696 --> 00:42:07,535
What gives?
Why didn't he invite me then?

861
00:42:07,896 --> 00:42:10,176
The organiser is an

862
00:42:10,176 --> 00:42:11,135
old client of mine.

863
00:42:11,135 --> 00:42:13,335
I'm going there to visit him mainly.

864
00:42:13,335 --> 00:42:15,095
I'm just joining the forum
since I'll be there anyway.

865
00:42:16,775 --> 00:42:19,176
I think you're just going there
to join the forum.

866
00:42:20,176 --> 00:42:21,135
Take me with you.

867
00:42:22,016 --> 00:42:23,375
A spy like me

868
00:42:23,375 --> 00:42:25,656
needs to head to the enemy's nest
to eradicate them once and for all.

869
00:42:27,176 --> 00:42:28,216
Take me with you.

870
00:42:28,216 --> 00:42:29,095
You're a renowned figure.

871
00:42:29,095 --> 00:42:30,656
You need to have a servant beside you.

872
00:42:31,375 --> 00:42:32,456
Besides,

873
00:42:32,936 --> 00:42:34,615
the mountain path is rugged and uneven.

874
00:42:35,176 --> 00:42:36,216
I checked the schedule too.

875
00:42:36,216 --> 00:42:37,016
We have to gather mugwort

876
00:42:37,016 --> 00:42:37,936
in the mountains before dawn
on the second day.

877
00:42:37,936 --> 00:42:39,375
I'm sure you'll depart at night.

878
00:42:39,375 --> 00:42:40,736
What if you encounter a bear

879
00:42:40,736 --> 00:42:42,775
or a robber? It'll be dangerous.

880
00:42:43,496 --> 00:42:44,696
Most importantly,

881
00:42:46,216 --> 00:42:47,176
it's a long journey.

882
00:42:47,216 --> 00:42:49,615
You need a second driver somehow.

883
00:42:56,862 --> 00:42:58,071
(The prescriptions and remedies
used in this drama)

884
00:42:58,260 --> 00:43:00,006
(are referenced from relevant
traditional Chinese medicine books)

885
00:43:00,220 --> 00:43:01,897
(Do not use without medical advice)
(End of Episode 9)

